{"type":null,"faqId":36266,"title":"是否支持手写输入？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{text-indent:-0.19722222in;margin-left:1.6381944in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.045138888in;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>平板默认的输入法是华为输入法，该输入法支持手写输入。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.2\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115667\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.2.1.1.1\"></a><span>请确保当前的输入法为华为输入法且屏幕键盘处于中文输入模式下。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.2.1.2.1\"></a><span>不同的版本华为输入法操作不同，下面的描述仅供参考。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.1.1\"></a><span>如果您的键盘布局如下图所示，点击键盘上的“</span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.1.1.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.1.1.1.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115668\" style=\"width:0.25in;height:0.17916666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，选择“手写”或“手写（全屏）”输入。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<a name=\"figd0e962\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115669\" style=\"width:5.5291667in;height:3.948611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.2.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.2.1\"></a><span>如果您的键盘布局如下图所示，点击键盘上的“</span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.2.1.1.1\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.2.1.1.1\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115670\" style=\"width:0.24930556in;height:0.18263888in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，选择带有手写输入面板的布局即可。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<a name=\"figd0e970\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115671\" style=\"width:5.5291667in;height:3.948611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.3.3.1\"></a><span>如果您的输入法布局如下图所示，点击“拼音”，选择“手写”，然后选择半屏手写或全屏手写。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<a name=\"figd0e981\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115672\" style=\"width:5.5291667in;height:3.948611in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<a name=\"gen-id1.4.7.2.4\"></a><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=115673\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span>所有图片仅供参考，具体操作请以实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":168,"faqType":"信息与电子邮件","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1286","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Messaging-Emailing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1438828321000,"seriesProductName":"T1-A23L","visitedTimes":10,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"手写,手写输入","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}